Class PegState

  • java.lang.Object
    • PegState
  • public class PegState
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is meant to represent a state in the game of peg solitaire. Moreover its used to keep track of what move to try next in the backtracking algorithm of PegSolitaireSolver
    Since:
    2020-09-23
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Nate
